    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------   \n\nOne of the folks over at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> just hit me up about a pile of cargo, <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> or smaller, that needs to be hauled out to a few different spots.   \n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)  \n~mission(SingleToMultiToken)  \n\nI'm trusting you to set your own route here, so don't mess it up. And try to stay away from anywhere too dangerous. And don't forget to pack a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to bring along.",
